title: [C#] Update carter to 5.2
body:
Updates the requirements on [Carter](https://github.com/CarterCommunity/Carter) to permit the latest version.
Commits
  • a231b14 use dotnet pack for template
  • 0d99120 Provide a message when Validate cannot resolve a Validator (#258)
  • f0a6b59 Create release-notes.yml
  • 3946cca Update and rename releasenotes.yml to release-notes.yml
  • 369a3ee Create releasenotes.yml
  • bb82189 Update README.md
  • 1ffe373 Change module scoped logger (#251)
  • b354830 Ignore case on form binding (#257)
  • bedd84f Make API version configurable (#256)
  • 0c63f12 - Switch to using the generic overload of IValidator.Validate to support Flue...
  • Additional commits viewable in compare view
